steps.name: the user select a result
the user is directed to deal page
the user visit the search car page

elements.name: Validate Text filter search (for Audi A4)

steps.name: the user search for a car
the car that the user searched is displayed
the user visit the search car page
the user click on inclusive benefits filter
the user choose a inclusive benefits filter
the chosen belongs to the selected inclusive benefits
the user uncheck a filter selected
the user click on make filter
the user choose a make filter
the chosen belongs to the selected make
the model filter is displayed
the user uncheck a filter selected
the user click on fuel filter
the user choose a fuel filter
the fuel chosen is displayed
the user uncheck a filter selected
the user click on drive filter
the user choose a drive filter
the drive chosen is displayed
the user uncheck a filter selected
the user click on style filter
the user choose a style filter
the style chosen is displayed
the user uncheck a filter selected
the user click on doors filter
the user choose a doors filter
the doors option chosen is displayed
the user uncheck a filter selected
the user click on seats filter
the user choose a seats filter
the seats filter chosen is displayed
the user uncheck a filter selected
the user click on engine filter
the user choose a engine option
the engine filter chosen is displayed
the user uncheck a filter selected
the user click on spec filter
the user choose a spec option
the spec filter chosen is displayed
the user visit the search car page
the user click on sort by filter
the user choose the filter
the sort by filter is selected
the user visit the search car page
the user click on clear filters button
the filters are successfully cleaned
the user visit the search car page
the user filters the search by low loco score
wait for the results load
the lowest score should appear
the user filters the search by high loco score
wait for the results load
the highest score should appear
the user visit the search car page
the user click on In Stock filter
the In Stock tag is displayed on search car page
the user choose a result
the chosen has the In Stock toggle selected
the user visit the search car page

the user click on find a deal button
the search result shows only personal lease type
the user visit the homepage

the user click on fuel filter
the user choose all fuel filters

the all fuel filters are deleted
the user visit the search car page
the user click on drive filter

the user click on all drive filters selected
the all drive filters are deleted
the user visit the search car page

the all style filters are deleted
the user visit the search car page
the user click on doors filter

the user visit the search car page
the user click on seats filter

the all seats Filters are deleted
the user visit the search car page
